'''仇恨團體'''（{{lang-en|Hate group}}）是針對某些人士的[[種族|種族]]、[[民族|民族]]、[[膚色|膚色]]、[[國籍|國籍]]、[[宗教|宗教]]、[[文化|文化]]、[[語言|語言]]、[[口音_(社會語言學)|口音]]、[[階級|階級]]、[[職業|職業]]、[[外貌|外貌]]、[[性別|性別]]、[[性取向|性取向]]、[[性別認同|性別認同]]及[[性別氣質|性別氣質]]等而[[憎恨|憎恨]]、討厭、敵視或者訴諸[[暴力|暴力]]的有組織集團。

[[美國|美國]]有兩個監察仇恨團體的主要組織，分別是[[反誹謗聯盟|反誹謗聯盟]]<ref name="titleADL: Fighting Anti-Semitism, Bigotry and Extremism">{{cite web |url=http://www.adl.org/ |title=ADL: Fighting Anti-Semitism, Bigotry and Extremism |accessdate=2008-04-13 |format= |work= |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524042237/http://www.adl.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[南方貧困法律中心|南方貧困法律中心]]<ref name="titleSPLCenter.org...forwarding to index.jsp">{{cite web |url=http://www.splcenter.org/ |title=SPLCenter.org...forwarding to index.jsp |accessdate=2008-04-13 |format= |work= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713171814/https://www.splcenter.org/ |archive-date=2019-07-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。除此之外，這些仇恨團體都被[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]追踪。此外，美國還有宗教性質的仇恨團體，相當一部分有[[基督新教|基督新教]]極端主義背景，包括[[3K黨|3K黨]]、[[天軍|天軍]]、[[威斯特布路浸信會|威斯特布路浸信會]]<ref>{{Cite document|title=Westboro Baptist Church|url=http://www.adl.org/learn/ext_us/WBC/default.asp?LEARN_Cat=Extremism&LEARN_SubCat=Extremism_in_America&xpicked=3&item=WBC|publisher=[[Anti-Defamation_League|Anti-Defamation League]]|postscript=|accessdate=June 20, 2010|journal=|archive-date=2010-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100707223315/http://www.adl.org/learn/ext_us/WBC/default.asp?LEARN_Cat=Extremism&LEARN_SubCat=Extremism_in_America&xpicked=3&item=WBC|dead-url=no}}
